display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A} = (a_{ij})]]></fr:tex> be a matrix over <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {C}]]></fr:tex>. We call <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A}]]></fr:tex> <html:dfn
