xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Self-Adjoint</html:dfn>) if it is equal to its complex-conjugate transpose:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[a_{ij} = \overline {a_{ji}}]]></fr:tex><fr:p>Or equivalently:</fr:p><fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A} = \overline {A^{\mathsf {T}}}]]></fr:tex></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter><fr:tree
